  "stemHtml": "<p>A revenue flight is to be made by a jet transport. The following are the aeroplane structural limits, masses and fuel load:</p><figure class=\"table\"><table><tbody><tr><td>Maximum Ramp Mass:</td><td style=\"text-align:right;\">69 900</td><td>kg</td></tr><tr><td>Maximum Take-off Mass:</td><td style=\"text-align:right;\">69 300</td><td>kg</td></tr><tr><td>Maximum Landing Mass:</td><td style=\"text-align:right;\">58 900</td><td>kg</td></tr><tr><td>Maximum Zero Fuel Mass:</td><td style=\"text-align:right;\">52 740</td><td>kg</td></tr><tr><td>Performance limited Take-off Mass:</td><td style=\"text-align:right;\">67 450</td><td>kg</td></tr><tr><td>Performance limited Landing Mass:</td><td style=\"text-align:right;\">55 470</td><td>kg</td></tr><tr><td> </td><td> </td><td> </td></tr><tr><td>Dry Operating Mass:</td><td style=\"text-align:right;\">34 900</td><td>kg</td></tr><tr><td>Trip Fuel:</td><td style=\"text-align:right;\">6200</td><td>kg</td></tr><tr><td>Taxi Fuel:</td><td style=\"text-align:right;\">250</td><td>kg</td></tr><tr><td>Contingency and final reserve fuel:</td><td style=\"text-align:right;\">1300</td><td>kg</td></tr><tr><td>Alternate Fuel:</td><td style=\"text-align:right;\">1100</td><td>kg</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>The maximum Traffic Load (TL) that can be carried is\u2026</p>",
